Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}心描き出す地図上の未知なるフロンティア
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}扉開いたら道は続いているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}埃巻き上げて 君の街へ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}空と大地が重なるルートで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}走る南風に乗って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}蒼く染まる風を切って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}心ごと駆けだしているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}真昼の月を追い越して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}昨日とは違う世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}どこまでも走り抜けてく あの風のように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}あの風のように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}心裡描繪著 地圖上的未知區域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}敞開心扉 路途繼續著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}喧揚起塵土 奔向你的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}馳騁在天地的交界線上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}乘上飛馳的南風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}穿越蔚藍色的清風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}心情雀躍不已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}追逐正午的明月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}向著與昨日不同的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}就像風一樣 無論何處都能到達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}就像那風一樣

Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.85,0:27:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}きっと君は今日の日も 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.90,0:28:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}真っ直ぐ明日を見てる 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.91,0:28:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}風が吹くあの丘に咲いた 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.62,0:28:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}向日葵のように 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.16,0:28:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}どんなに遠く離れていても 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.22,0:28:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}この歌声が君に届くように 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.17,0:28:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}涙がずっと止まらない夜 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.20,0:28:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}君の窓を照らす月になりたい 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.54,0:28:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}また必ず会えると そう思うから
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.85,0:27:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}你今天一定也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.90,0:28:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}直視著明天
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.91,0:28:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}彷彿在那微風吹過的山丘上
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.62,0:28:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}綻放的向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.16,0:28:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}即使相離再遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.22,0:28:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}也要把這歌聲傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.17,0:28:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}在這滿臉淚痕的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.20,0:28:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}希望成為照亮你窗前的月光
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.54,0:28:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}一定會再相見的 我這麼相信著

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------------Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥她…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介 不好意思 我們跟蹤你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪奧他們正在和Venom交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且尚未有任何有效的對抗手段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才把坐標通知了Danaan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要把Arblest發射到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去我們沒勝算的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這你應該最清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓千鳥死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓自己被殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還剩下什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小姐 她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來就沒有過未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自自相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自的死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類不過是行屍走肉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的話和那些恐怖份子一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你已經不是我們的夥伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去靈魂的戰士只不過是個殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把他留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送那種東西來也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也使不動那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想去用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 就這樣在那裡腐爛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在問你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊你個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千…鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥你個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還…活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什你個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我費這麼大心思跑來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才還打算象電視裡那樣飛進你的懷抱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你還活著啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一下子就沒心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎麼補償我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎麼對現在這個情況負責
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等 千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒聽明白你的意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛吧 很痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我心靈的傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是我肉體的傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這是我靈魂的傷痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要說什…到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還要問?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來帶你回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被折磨的死去活來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於決定坦白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是 我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學…學生會委員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還沒過一天就動搖了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經聽那個狩人的大叔說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪奧姐他們都在戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法操縱那個機體了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我…還把你扔下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不能發揮力量麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把一切都拋棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能說出來過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介總是太認真 娘娘腔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你什麼都做不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懦弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很沒用 但是總能想出辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為你是這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱者會寄生在強者身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和弱小的傢伙們混一起開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還廢話什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很危險了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有學校的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點給我去解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PASS-1呼叫Uruz1
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向南方3區退離
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法將它引開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人也應該累了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果耗盡她的體力的話就能贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要她會耗盡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…讓我…太費神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz1呼叫PASS-1
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裡是PASS-1 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Venom…出現了5架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見面了啊 小玉芳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我在預定外的區域擅自搞破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不計劃性的發動戰爭是不行的 不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣讓我們非常難堪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我們失去故鄉的那場內戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也是Amalgam在背後操縱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能向你們復仇的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和妹妹就算死也值得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有位特邀嘉賓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 登場亮相
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 是你妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你我專程帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像不怎麼有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小玉蘭 你到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被強大的性感的蓋斯大人抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不幸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為總算和姐姐見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 是嗎 太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 姐姐 快停止戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糾紛是不能解決任何事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最後被蓋斯大人給玷污了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉 好像斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太嫩了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那邊的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Mirthril的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然今天沒你們的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能算你運氣不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的小羊羔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該做的都做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就走好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰射擊的 維伯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他總算來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還在這個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不感覺太美味了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz7呼叫各機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arblest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才發動了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,λ-Driver確實發動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時而發動時而熄火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個糟糕的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像比我更擅長開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連粗活也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PASS-1呼叫Uruz7
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復正常了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就放開打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Venom5架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般情況下就應該逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們能行 中士閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我們上!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是一架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這高度怎麼可能 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近警告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3架了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搶在我前面說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 別過來 別過來 別過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺了 駕駛員了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mirthril的λ-Driver不是不穩定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想知道的話 我就告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mirthril怎麼的 完全無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…東京都立陳代高中2年4班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 我這裡還有人質呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學號41號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責倒垃圾兼放雨傘的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良宗介!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是短了些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過要相信自己的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你這也做的太過頭了 中士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的高威脅性目標全擊毀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中士 我有個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的戰鬥各方面看來都是非常驚人的戰果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 可以把這理由告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:18:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是解決了些問題 這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我們的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白你回答的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想吧 搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz7呼叫全單位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Venom全都擊破了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來返回Tuatha de Danaan…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修正
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始 Uruz7將進行新的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arblest我扔下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們自己回收下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快些的話 會被當地軍隊發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼 下一個任務是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上 通訊完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又要違反命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 就是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 這樣也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成了誰都沒預料到的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不能無視那個機體的潛能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是她賜予了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個士兵和那藝術品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之香港沒變成火海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良和千鳥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像回東京了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違反命令啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把她帶來的你也同罪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 就交給上層部判斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這種威脅似的方式來反抗我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒有如此憤怒過 中士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿米特將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能駕駛Arblest的只有他一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你閉嘴 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為情報部部長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人提出的條件不予以採納
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下只是提出改變合同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:20:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您不滿意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下將付違約金 退出這個部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真敢說出口啊 中士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為與我為敵 你今後還想有好日子過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我直說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真認為我連這點覺悟都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒記得把自己的靈魂一起賣給Mirthril了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要以自己的做法活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我也會駕駛Arblest
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要讓我上那個學校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如以往一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只要付我一半工資即可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有什麼不滿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意你的用詞 中士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中士? 我不過是個傭兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我這種侯鳥說這個沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這些話說給自己養的狗去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小子!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬羅里長官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你輸了 將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一名擁有寶貴技能的STR成員說只要一半工資就肯幹活了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有什麼理由生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人還有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯特羅莎上校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是些這麼有特點的部下一定很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我的部下是最傑出的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 中士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫 相良·宗介吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會記住你的名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次會議 就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那各位保重了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇出我一身冷汗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別給我增添負擔了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始有點男人的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.70,0:22:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會我BG
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候真的抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的事 要道歉的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.50,0:22:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.40,0:22:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記了立場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是我太任性了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:22:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.10,0:23:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你認為我是朋友的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能恕我說幾句冒犯的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.60,0:23:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰蕾莎 一直都很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.80,0:23:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個很了不起的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.50,0:23:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我來說不只是個上司
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.00,0:23:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為是個更重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.30,0:23:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…如果有什麼事情的話 我一定會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:23:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此你一定要記住…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.80,0:24:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起 果然還是太冒犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是我的真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.70,0:24:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.60,0:24:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰蕾莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰蕾莎 他叫我 泰蕾莎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.40,0:24:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.00,0:24:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說我是很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.70,0:24:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.00,0:24:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老這樣的話 就算我也很難包庇你的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.40,0:24:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.50,0:24:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好是扣在我這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.80,0:24:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次我汽車的事情也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.10,0:24:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去…小心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.80,0:24:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 你要幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.40,0:24:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.60,0:24:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被激光器瞄準了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.80,0:24:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.60,0:24:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊 宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.40,0:24:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臥倒 千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.30,0:24:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有激光器對著我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.60,0:24:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 活該
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.10,0:25:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是在西北風下監視呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.90,0:25:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點惡作劇就…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.40,0:25:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要冬天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.80,0:25:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你一回來就會弄點事情出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.90,0:25:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這叫我怎麼和老師解釋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.80,0:25:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.40,0:25:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要找藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.80,0:25:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是一點沒進步
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.30,0:25:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是 總是 總是 總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.60,0:25:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是 總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.50,0:25:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是…總是 總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.60,0:25:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下…總算是恢復往常了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.60,0:25:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.90,0:25:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣把我扔下逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.50,0:25:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.50,0:25:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.90,0:25:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.00,0:26:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉就好了嗎 笨蛋 笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.70,0:26:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.50,0:26:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.70,0:26:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.10,0:26:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.00,0:26:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.80,0:26:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 小要和相良同學
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.10,0:26:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個人在這裡幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.70,0:26:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.70,0:26:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.60,0:26:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 難道說小要在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.50,0:26:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介他…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.80,0:27:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良是不是你又慌稱有炸彈 趁機吃小要豆腐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.90,0:27:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你說
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.20,0:27:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢是不找借口的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.40,0:27:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真是差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.50,0:27:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.20,0:27:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.30,0:27:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.30,0:27:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.00,0:27:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.20,0:29:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.10,0:29:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在香港的時候你好像要對我說什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.40,0:29:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.00,0:29:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.30,0:29:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.90,0:29:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…



